From: SANYS)"

Subject: 
Update 
Date: Tue, 03 Sep 2019 22:32:38 +0000 
Importance: Normal 
• 
Not much to report. 
In Epstein, interviews planned for today in Florida were postponed due to weather. 
In MCC, two inmates across from Epstein's cell were supposed to be interviewed. One declined the interview and the 
other had nothing of interest to contribute. He slept through the night and only saw the activities in the morning after 
Epstein was found in his cell. 
Feel free to call me if you have any questions. 
United States Attorney's Office 
Southern District of New York 
EFTA00023225
